Sentencas: The fabrication of stereoscopic anode with high porosity is essential for the effective use of natural gas as fuel in solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Fabrication of Ni0.5Cu0.5Ox coated YSZ anode by hard template method for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The tubular YSZ coated by Ni0.5Cu0.5Ox was prepared by hard template method combined with wet impregnation method.
Titulo: Fabrication of Ni0.5Cu0.5Ox coated YSZ anode by hard template method for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: YSZ electrolyte-supported single cell was fabricated by using Ni0.5Cu0.5Ox-YSZ as anode for the power generation performance test and the long-term stability test.
Titulo: Fabrication of Ni0.5Cu0.5Ox coated YSZ anode by hard template method for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The surface composition and microstructure of anode were further analyzed by SEM and EDS after 100 h test.
Titulo: Fabrication of Ni0.5Cu0.5Ox coated YSZ anode by hard template method for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The maximum power densities of 315.52 and 241.77 mW cm(-2) were achieved under dry methane and wet methane (3% H2O) at 800 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Fabrication of Ni0.5Cu0.5Ox coated YSZ anode by hard template method for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The voltage was stable even after tested for 100 h with the fuel of wet methane.
Titulo: Fabrication of Ni0.5Cu0.5Ox coated YSZ anode by hard template method for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The SEM observation of the tested anode showed that the tubular YSZ had hollow structure, in which both internal and external surfaces were coated by Ni0.5Cu0.5 alloy particles, resulting a stable structure.
Titulo: Fabrication of Ni0.5Cu0.5Ox coated YSZ anode by hard template method for solid oxide fuel cells
